&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with data mesh, data lakehouse, or data fabric paradigms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deeper back-end engineering experience (Node.js, Python, or similar) beyond familiarity—able to own backend components when needed.&lt;/li&gt;
